you physically can't.

9
00:01:16,209 --> 00:01:18,143
Going to work?

10
00:01:18,344 --> 00:01:19,777
Yeah, work.

11
00:01:19,946 --> 00:01:22,881
- Sorry about waking you.
- What time is it?

12
00:01:23,049 --> 00:01:26,883
- 6:30.
- Jesus. Why so early?

13
00:01:27,087 --> 00:01:29,351
I got a brief due, so...

14
00:01:29,489 --> 00:01:31,457
There was nothing brief about it.

15
00:01:31,591 --> 00:01:34,560
Steve and Miranda had been doing
the polite avoid-each-other

16
00:01:34,694 --> 00:01:36,491
