17
00:01:37,931 --> 00:01:39,899
I'm sorry it's taking me so long

18
00:01:40,033 --> 00:01:41,660
to find a place.

19
00:01:41,801 --> 00:01:43,769
I got a lead on one, though.

20
00:01:43,903 --> 00:01:45,598
OK.

21
00:01:45,738 --> 00:01:49,435
Hey, do you... Never mind.

22
00:01:49,609 --> 00:01:50,974
