23
00:01:51,111 --> 00:01:53,739
I was gonna ask if you'd look at it
with me,

24
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:56,314
but that's weird, right?

25
00:01:56,483 --> 00:02:00,419
- I don't know. We could do that.
- Yeah?

26
00:02:04,991 --> 00:02:07,357
When you find that place to move,

27
00:02:07,527 --> 00:02:09,495
you need to fill it with furniture.

28
00:02:09,662 --> 00:02:11,960
