of the New Designer showcase.

30
00:02:17,437 --> 00:02:19,234
I'm like your roady.

31
00:02:19,405 --> 00:02:22,306
I don't have a road.
I just have this booth.

32
00:02:22,475 --> 00:02:27,310
- At best, you're my booth-bitch.
- Yeah, I'm your booth-bitch.

33
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:29,345
I wax your wood.

34
00:02:29,549 --> 00:02:32,313
