This is the designer.
This is Aidan Shaw.

53
00:04:05,478 --> 00:04:07,673
Great stuff.

54
00:04:07,847 --> 00:04:09,508
Thanks, man.

55
00:04:11,284 --> 00:04:13,411
- Oak?
- It's mostly maple.

56
00:04:13,586 --> 00:04:17,352
There we were. Mostly maple
and incredibly uncomfortable.

57
00:04:17,523 --> 00:04:20,720
- Sorry, I didn't get your names.
- Oh, I'm sorry.

58
00:04:20,893 --> 00:04:23,555
These are my friends.

59
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:26,358
This is Natasha, and this is...

60
